# questkit-worker-webhook-consumer local secrets.
# Copy to `.dev.vars` (gitignored) for `wrangler dev`. This worker has no
# direct secrets — it relies on the `API` service binding to reach
# questkit-worker-api, which owns the JWT/HMAC/APP secrets. Kept here for
# parity with the other workers so `env-sync` doesn't flag a missing file.
